1
00:01:09,780 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,740 --> 00:01:17,700
=Episode 17=
(Double Blow)

3
00:01:17,799 --> 00:01:18,519
Miss Lin

4
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:19,879
is a well-known influencer
who exposes scams.

5
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:21,519
She is accusing us,

6
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:23,280
claiming there is a camera in her room.

7
00:01:23,959 --> 00:01:25,480
The views have already hit a million.

8
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:26,400
It's making a storm.

9
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,280
Qingmei,

10
00:01:27,439 --> 00:01:29,200
your resort is really bustling.

11
00:01:29,359 --> 00:01:31,200
Shaoze and I wanted to sleep in,

12
00:01:31,439 --> 00:01:33,359
but the noise woke us up early.

13
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:36,159
Did Mr. Mu stay at our resort
last night?

14
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:38,120
Yes.

15
00:01:38,319 --> 00:01:39,680
Last night was exhausting.

16
00:01:40,239 --> 00:01:41,560
I need to go back and catch up on sleep.

17
00:01:42,439 --> 00:01:43,400
Let's go, Shaoze.

18
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:52,560
Everyone,

19
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:55,959
there could be more cameras anywhere!

20
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:58,799
Let's check out what is happening.

21
00:01:59,319 --> 00:01:59,760
Oh, by the way,

22
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:01,400
get two reporters over here.

23
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:02,760
Already taken care of.
They are on the way.

24
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:04,239
What if someone got filmed

25
00:02:04,439 --> 00:02:05,560
and it got spread online?

26
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:06,280
Perfect.

27
00:02:07,439 --> 00:02:07,920
Everyone,

28
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,439
this is no exaggeration.

29
00:02:09,639 --> 00:02:11,639
Whether you are traveling
or staying overnight,

30
00:02:11,759 --> 00:02:13,919
protect your privacy.

31
00:02:14,919 --> 00:02:16,919
Privacy is no trivial thing.

32
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,319
Who are you?

33
00:02:19,919 --> 00:02:21,800
I am Gu Qingmei,
Chairman of Gu Corporation.

34
00:02:22,159 --> 00:02:24,240
Regarding Miss Lin's privacy concerns,

35
00:02:24,639 --> 00:02:26,639
we have another
professional way of recording.

36
00:02:32,879 --> 00:02:34,000
To ensure fairness and truthfulness,

37
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,280
our entire process

38
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:37,960
will be open to
the public and the media.

39
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,319
Everyone knows

40
00:02:41,719 --> 00:02:43,639
I used to be a journalist.

41
00:02:44,080 --> 00:02:46,000
Using this kind of tactic against me

42
00:02:46,319 --> 00:02:47,479
is underestimating me.

43
00:02:47,599 --> 00:02:49,240
You used to be a journalist?

44
00:02:49,479 --> 00:02:51,400
Then you should know that
anything shared publicly

45
00:02:51,879 --> 00:02:53,199
requires solid evidence.

46
00:02:54,159 --> 00:02:55,280
I do have evidence.

47
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:58,000
Everyone in the livestream saw it.

48
00:02:58,120 --> 00:03:00,039
I found a camera in this room.

49
00:03:00,879 --> 00:03:01,960
If you don't believe me,

50
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,280
you can watch the replay.

51
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:04,400
Alright.

52
00:03:04,719 --> 00:03:05,560
If it is true,

53
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:07,439
I will be accountable to
you and the public.

54
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,840
But if it is fake,

55
00:03:09,319 --> 00:03:11,080
I will hold you fully accountable
on behalf of Gu Corporation.

56
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:12,879
Mr. Chen,

57
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:13,960
send someone

58
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,879
to inspect every room in the resort.

59
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:16,599
Yes.

60
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,319
Everyone,

61
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,280
they refuse to admit it.

62
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:28,560
Let me tell you,

63
00:03:28,759 --> 00:03:29,879
this hotel is terrible.

64
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,159
Don't ever come here!

65
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,439
Make sure to check thoroughly.

66
00:03:32,759 --> 00:03:34,439
Under the TV, outlets...

67
00:03:35,159 --> 00:03:36,520
those are all blind spots.

68
00:03:37,439 --> 00:03:39,120
Carefully. Hurry up.

69
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,599
Madam Gu, nothing found.

70
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,280
Madam Gu,

71
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:57,680
out of all the rooms in the resort,

72
00:03:57,759 --> 00:03:59,919
only Room 403,
where Miss Lin is staying,

73
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:00,919
had a camera.

74
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,039
She must have staged it herself.

75
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,199
Apparently,

76
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:06,240
her livestream yesterday gained
over a hundred thousand followers.

77
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,400
Looks like she came prepared.

78
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:10,919
I have a feeling this goes deeper.

79
00:04:11,919 --> 00:04:13,120
Something is off.

80
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:15,400
Should I send someone to her?

81
00:04:15,599 --> 00:04:16,160
No.

82
00:04:16,639 --> 00:04:18,120
Before we have solid evidence,

83
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:19,319
don't tip her off.

84
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:20,839
We don't want to give her leverage.

85
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:30,160
Check the surveillance
at the entrance of Room 403

86
00:04:30,439 --> 00:04:31,480
and see who has been around there.

87
00:04:32,079 --> 00:04:32,519
Alright.

88
00:04:38,199 --> 00:04:39,519
Boss, that's too much.

89
00:04:39,639 --> 00:04:40,519
No more drinking.

90
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:43,439
I should go home and get some sleep too.

91
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,319
Finish that and you can go.

92
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,319
Hold on.

93
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,920
Miss Su, help!

94
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:53,920
If you don't come now,

95
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,480
someone is going to
drink himself to death.

96
00:05:02,079 --> 00:05:02,920
Don't disturb her.

97
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,079
I let her down.

98
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,519
I should not have done that.

99
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:13,839
I never realized

100
00:05:14,319 --> 00:05:15,800
my boss is a coward

101
00:05:16,399 --> 00:05:17,319
and a chatterbox.

102
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:26,439
Hello.

103
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:27,120
Boss,

104
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,560
as you expected,

105
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,480
the influencer
who caused trouble at the resort

106
00:05:30,639 --> 00:05:31,879
was sent by He Jinchen.

107
00:05:32,279 --> 00:05:34,000
He wants to ruin the resort's reputation

108
00:05:34,279 --> 00:05:35,240
and force a low-price acquisition.

109
00:05:36,519 --> 00:05:38,000
Take down that trending post.

110
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:39,399
Also,

111
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,600
send someone to negotiate
with that influencer.

112
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,199
Besides,

113
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,399
don't let Su Li know.

114
00:05:45,759 --> 00:05:46,600
Alright, boss.

115
00:05:51,279 --> 00:05:51,800
Boss,

116
00:05:52,639 --> 00:05:53,920
you care so much about Miss Su.

117
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:55,160
Why are you avoiding her?

118
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:58,800
You two just slept together.

119
00:05:58,879 --> 00:06:00,000
We are all adults.

120
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:00,600
Get out!

121
00:06:04,279 --> 00:06:04,800
Alright.

122
00:06:11,839 --> 00:06:12,399
I found something.

123
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,120
Look.

124
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,759
This person looks suspicious.

125
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:15,480
But

126
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:16,560
he is well disguised.

127
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:17,920
In our database,

128
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,199
I could not find a match

129
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,319
with any employee records.

130
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:21,920
Any distinguishing features?

131
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:22,800
Features?

132
00:06:22,959 --> 00:06:23,879
Look,

133
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:24,959
his shoes.

134
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:27,839
They are a pair of branded sneakers.

135
00:06:27,879 --> 00:06:29,079
Branded sneakers?

136
00:06:34,879 --> 00:06:36,000
Quick, take him down!

137
00:06:36,279 --> 00:06:37,000
Let me go!

138
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:38,360
Hold still! Take him down!

139
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,600
I didn't do anything!

140
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,399
Did you install the camera in Room 403?

141
00:06:43,519 --> 00:06:44,199
I'll talk. I'll tell you everything!

142
00:06:44,439 --> 00:06:44,959
It was me.

143
00:06:45,839 --> 00:06:47,680
I installed the camera in the room.

144
00:06:48,879 --> 00:06:50,439
Everyone, the truth is out!

145
00:06:50,759 --> 00:06:52,240
The hotel employee

146
00:06:52,279 --> 00:06:53,240
installed the camera

147
00:06:53,399 --> 00:06:54,519
to spy on guests' privacy

148
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,920
and profit from it online.

149
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,079
This is disgusting!

150
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:59,000
Everyone, I strongly urge

151
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:00,920
that this hotel be
shut down immediately!

152
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:01,759
Breaking news.

153
00:07:02,199 --> 00:07:03,000
Yunhu Resort

154
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:05,000
has been ordered to suspend operations
due to privacy violations.

155
00:07:05,199 --> 00:07:06,319
Here are the details.

156
00:07:06,519 --> 00:07:07,279
What is going on?

157
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,519
How could such a big scandal break?

158
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,399
Tell Gu Qingmei

159
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,360
that she represents
not just the Gu family,

160
00:07:16,879 --> 00:07:18,279
but also the He family
as our daughter-in-law.

161
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,319
Tell her to come back

162
00:07:20,639 --> 00:07:22,160
and stay out of the public eye.

163
00:07:26,199 --> 00:07:26,720
Yes, Dad.

164
00:07:27,319 --> 00:07:28,160
I will go find her now.

165
00:07:36,759 --> 00:07:37,199
Madam Gu,

166
00:07:37,199 --> 00:07:38,519
do you have any comment

167
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,519
on the privacy leak?

168
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:40,639
The resort is deleting trending posts.

169
00:07:40,639 --> 00:07:42,199
Are you trying to cover up the truth?

170
00:07:42,279 --> 00:07:43,240
Can you explain, Madam Gu?

171
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:43,920
Please explain, Madam Gu!

172
00:07:43,959 --> 00:07:44,720
This is causing consumer panic.

173
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,040
Does the resort have a solution?

174
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:46,959
Will you do an interview?

175
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,759
Gu Corporation has always put
our customers first.

176
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:57,040
We never infringe on anyone's privacy.

177
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,160
Regarding this camera incident,

178
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:00,920
I will get to the bottom of it
within three days

179
00:08:01,279 --> 00:08:02,079
and give everyone an answer.

180
00:08:07,839 --> 00:08:08,399
Madam Gu,

181
00:08:08,399 --> 00:08:09,839
Madam Gu, any comment?

182
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,079
Give our money back!

183
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:12,879
What is going on here?

184
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:13,759
Pay us back!

185
00:08:18,639 --> 00:08:20,399
He Jinchen is behind all these.

186
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,040
I will help you fix it.

187
00:08:22,839 --> 00:08:23,720
Don't act rashly.

188
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,000
I don't need your help.

189
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:28,279
You know how ruthless He Jinchen is.

190
00:08:29,319 --> 00:08:30,480
Human life means nothing to him.

191
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,480
Who are you to meddle in my affairs?

192
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:38,320
As a shareholder of Gu Corporation,

193
00:08:39,159 --> 00:08:40,360
I don't want you to be in danger.

194
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:41,879
Mu Shaoze,

195
00:08:42,399 --> 00:08:43,799
I'm giving you one last chance.

196
00:08:44,039 --> 00:08:45,679
Explain your relationship with He Jinxi.

197
00:08:48,519 --> 00:08:49,440
There is nothing to explain.

198
00:08:50,679 --> 00:08:51,720
What matters now

199
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,840
is getting leverage
over Meiyan International

200
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,519
and evidence of their crimes.

201
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:56,919
I don't agree.

202
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:59,000
If I cannot even protect the resort,

203
00:08:59,159 --> 00:09:00,679
how can I fight He Jinchen?

204
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:02,840
I will not let him win.

205
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,440
If you have made up your mind,

206
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,080
let me handle it.

207
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:11,480
Take a few days off

208
00:09:11,759 --> 00:09:12,919
and let the media frenzy die down.

209
00:09:14,039 --> 00:09:14,519
Mr. Mu,

210
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:16,440
we're on different paths.

211
00:09:16,919 --> 00:09:17,960
Our partnership is over.

212
00:09:18,639 --> 00:09:19,720
From now on, you go your way,

213
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,039
I'll go mine.

214
00:09:21,799 --> 00:09:22,440
Qingmei.

215
00:09:26,519 --> 00:09:28,440
We heard about what happened
at the resort.

216
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:29,559
We were worried you might be stressed.

217
00:09:29,919 --> 00:09:31,480
Dad asked me to pick you up.

218
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:33,360
I'm fine.

219
00:09:33,879 --> 00:09:35,200
I have a meeting this afternoon.

220
00:09:35,399 --> 00:09:36,360
I'll go home after that.

221
00:09:40,559 --> 00:09:43,120
You may also go home with Jinxi tonight.

222
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:44,720
Dad wants to discuss something with you.

223
00:09:46,639 --> 00:09:47,080
Alright.

224
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,159
Look at this now.

225
00:09:58,399 --> 00:10:00,000
The resort's reputation
is completely ruined.

226
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:00,600
Exactly.

227
00:10:00,759 --> 00:10:01,879
The resort has been shut down,

228
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:03,159
and the stock has hit the limit down.

229
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,399
Who's going to be held accountable?

230
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:07,480
Someone is behind this.

231
00:10:08,039 --> 00:10:09,480
I'll find out who is pulling the strings

232
00:10:09,919 --> 00:10:10,639
and turn this around.

233
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:12,039
A narrow-minded view.

234
00:10:12,879 --> 00:10:14,440
You keep clinging to the resort

235
00:10:15,159 --> 00:10:17,000
and dragging all of us down with you.

236
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,320
At this point,

237
00:10:18,759 --> 00:10:20,720
the priority is
preventing further damage

238
00:10:21,159 --> 00:10:23,279
and finding a solution.

239
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:24,720
Now,

240
00:10:25,039 --> 00:10:26,480
let us take a vote

241
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:27,440
on whether Gu Qingmei

242
00:10:28,519 --> 00:10:29,759
should continue serving

243
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:31,759
as Chairman of Gu Corporation.

244
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:34,720
All shareholders in favor

245
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:36,919
of removing Gu Qingmei's position,

246
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:37,679
please raise your hands.

247
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:40,679
What could a woman possibly achieve?

248
00:10:41,519 --> 00:10:43,799
We won't let her keep fooling us.

249
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:46,080
I agree.

250
00:10:46,639 --> 00:10:47,279
I agree too.

251
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:48,559
I agree.

252
00:10:48,679 --> 00:10:49,200
I agree.

253
00:10:51,519 --> 00:10:52,039
I agree.

254
00:10:56,799 --> 00:10:59,039
Our group cannot function
without a leader.

255
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:02,120
We need to elect the next chairman.

256
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:06,519
Besides Gu Qingmei,

257
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:09,240
I am the second largest shareholder.

258
00:11:10,679 --> 00:11:11,240
Sorry to interrupt.

259
00:11:12,159 --> 00:11:12,600
Everyone.

260
00:11:13,279 --> 00:11:15,600
Since Gu Corporation's stock
has been crashing,

261
00:11:16,279 --> 00:11:16,799
I

262
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,120
happened to acquire

263
00:11:18,279 --> 00:11:19,600
twenty-five percent

264
00:11:19,679 --> 00:11:20,600
of the shares.

265
00:11:21,799 --> 00:11:22,679
Now I am

266
00:11:22,879 --> 00:11:24,840
the second largest shareholder
after Madam Gu.

267
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:28,120
Impossible!

268
00:11:28,759 --> 00:11:30,000
Now I am the most qualified

269
00:11:30,679 --> 00:11:32,279
to be Chairman of the Gu Corporation.

270
00:11:32,679 --> 00:11:33,320
I disagree.

271
00:11:33,519 --> 00:11:34,279
I disagree too.

272
00:11:39,180 --> 00:11:39,600
(Exposed Documents)

273
00:11:41,639 --> 00:11:42,120
Mr. Wang,

274
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:43,919
Mr. Liang,

275
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:46,159
you colluded in financial fraud

276
00:11:46,519 --> 00:11:47,600
and accepted commercial bribes.

277
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:49,480
Explain yourselves.

278
00:11:54,679 --> 00:11:55,279
Ridiculous!

279
00:11:55,879 --> 00:11:57,519
How do we know you are not framing us?

280
00:11:58,720 --> 00:11:59,639
That is fine.

281
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:01,519
I have already submitted the evidence

282
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:03,399
to the court.

283
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:05,960
If the evidence holds up,

284
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:07,679
you will be receiving subpoenas soon.

285
00:12:09,159 --> 00:12:10,039
Well...

286
00:12:15,399 --> 00:12:16,240
I support Mr. Mu.

287
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:17,519
With Mr. Mu leading us,

288
00:12:17,759 --> 00:12:18,639
there will be no problems.

289
00:12:20,919 --> 00:12:21,519
I support Mr. Mu!

290
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:22,159
Yes!

291
00:12:22,279 --> 00:12:23,399
We support Mr. Mu!

292
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:23,919
Yes!

293
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:26,919
Yes! We support Mr. Mu!

294
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,000
We support Mr. Mu!

295
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:28,759
Meeting adjourned.

296
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:30,600
Sure, sure.

297
00:12:51,399 --> 00:12:52,440
Everything you did

298
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:54,240
was to become

299
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:56,240
the chairman yourself.

300
00:12:57,919 --> 00:12:58,919
Eight years of preparation.

301
00:12:59,879 --> 00:13:01,519
I cannot afford any mistakes.

302
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:03,720
So I was just part of your plan too?

303
00:13:06,559 --> 00:13:07,759
A partner?

304
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:09,799
You never saw me

305
00:13:09,919 --> 00:13:11,080
as an equal.

306
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:12,679
You never trusted me.

307
00:13:13,159 --> 00:13:14,960
I just did not want you
getting involved with the resort.

308
00:13:16,279 --> 00:13:17,080
I want to protect you.

309
00:13:17,279 --> 00:13:18,639
Whether I am chairman or not,

310
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:20,399
for the matters of the resort,

311
00:13:20,799 --> 00:13:22,559
I will handle it my own way.

312
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:26,840
I don't need any man's help.

313
00:13:54,460 --> 00:13:59,220
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

314
00:13:59,220 --> 00:14:04,060
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

315
00:14:04,060 --> 00:14:08,620
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

316
00:14:08,620 --> 00:14:13,540
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

317
00:14:13,540 --> 00:14:17,340
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

318
00:14:17,340 --> 00:14:22,140
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

319
00:14:22,140 --> 00:14:24,980
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

320
00:14:24,980 --> 00:14:27,660
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

321
00:14:28,020 --> 00:14:33,580
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

322
00:14:33,980 --> 00:14:40,780
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

323
00:14:41,060 --> 00:14:45,740
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

324
00:14:45,900 --> 00:14:52,700
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

325
00:14:53,020 --> 00:14:59,820
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

326
00:15:00,020 --> 00:15:04,500
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

327
00:15:04,500 --> 00:15:07,860
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

328
00:15:07,860 --> 00:15:14,780
♪Right as I confess my love♪
